@doctordns `$FormatEnumerationLimit` is a preference variable. It is documented at https://docs.microsoft.com/powershell/module/microsoft.powershell.core/about/about_preference_variables#formatenumerationlimit

Your suggestion to add a parameter would affect the enumeration for all properties in the output. The suggestion from @jhoneill allows you to specify a different enumeration limit for each property.   

